word_mean_info__list.difference: 指停留或延续的时间很短。
普通用词，其反义是permanent。指持续有限的可计时间，着重暂时的存在、应用或效应。
指瞬时即逝的，也表明间很短的。

bilingual.source: She found a temporary solution to the problem.
bilingual.target: 她找到了一个暂时的解决方案。

bilingual.source: The temporary bridge will be replaced next year.
bilingual.target: 这座暂时的桥梁将在明年被替换。
这种药物可能会引起暂时的迷失方向感。

bilingual.source: The temporary exhibit will be on display for two weeks.
bilingual.target: 这个暂时的展览将展出两周。

bilingual.source: Music can provide a temporary escapism from daily stress.
bilingual.target: 音乐可以提供暂时的逃避现实，缓解日常压力。

bilingual.source: The medication may cause temporary impairment of motor skills.
bilingual.target: 这种药物可能会导致暂时的运动技能损伤。

bilingual.source: The company hired a temporary worker to cover the busy season.
bilingual.target: 公司雇佣了一名暂时的工人来应对繁忙季节。

bilingual.source: She viewed the failure as a temporary setback rather than a defeat.
bilingual.target: 她把失败看作是暂时的挫折而不是失败。

bilingual.source: He is staying in a temporary accommodation until his house is ready.
bilingual.target: 他暂时住在一个暂时的住所，直到他的房子准备好。
它们只能带来暂时的快乐。

list.abstract: 《Temporary》是日本歌手w-inds.演唱的歌曲。由Keita Tachibana、Chica作词，Keita Tachibana、Joe Ogawa作曲，收录在w-inds.2018年7月11日发行的专辑《100》中。

yingyinNormal.en: Everything around us, including the girl. Everything is temporary. We are forever.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们身边的一切，包括那个女孩。都是暂时的。我们才是永恒。

yingyinNormal.en: It's just temporary; I pay rent. He lives in the same room where his bassinet was.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只是暂时的，我有付房租。他现在的房间就是以前放婴儿床的。

yingyinNormal.en: I couldn't stay forever, you know. There's only supposed to be a temporary thing. It's okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道我不可能永远陪着你，这些都只是暂时的。嗯，我知道。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, I can see that. Are these just temporary? They're gonna look great. Just give us a week.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是，我能看出来，这只是暂时的吧。这里会变得很棒的，给我们一周。

yingyinNormal.en: At full capacity, it's the temporary home to more than 90,000 prime beef steers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在全力运转的情况下，它能暂时容纳九万多头肉牛。

yingyinNormal.en: But Rach, wasn't this supposed to a temporary thing? I thought you wanted to do fashion stuff?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不是暂时性的工作而已吗？你的目标是打入时装界。

yingyinNormal.en: What the hell is this? Boilerplate stuff. A modified roommate agreement for a temporary house guest.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这又是什么东东？都是些陈辞滥调啦，针对临时住客的改良版室友协议。

yingyinNormal.en: And it's only temporary, just till I get back on my feet. or the baby goes off to college, whichever happens first.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只是暂时借住而已，待我站稳脚跟。东山再起，或是宝宝要去上大学了，看哪件事先发生吧。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm sorry, I was reassigned to this project. I was told you were taking a temporary sabbatical to focus on other work.
yingyinNormal.zh: 抱歉，我被分配到这个项目。他们说你要暂时休假去忙别的研究。

yingyinNormal.en: We built the Tet, our mission control, a temporary space station before the migration to Titan, Saturn's largest moon.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们建造了泰特，作为指挥中心，也是移民泰坦前的临时太空站，泰坦是土星最大的卫星。

yingyinNormal.en: I would love to be around for you and the baby. And we can just try it like on a temporary basis. But Ross, its you and me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很乐意照顾你跟宝宝，我们可试试看，先试一阵子。但那是你跟我。
